Oh yeah, and you think tash is a big aggro?  Try tash followed by a nook!  I don't think there's anything that aggros more than a chantanook. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Anyhow so use those sparingly and at the end of the fight, and they can be good for the group. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img src="http://www.annastazia.homestead.com/files/adjani.jpg" alt="Adjani Tristesse, Goddess of Lanys"></img>
